      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the highly desirable 3.8L DFI flat-six engine producing 385 hp and 310 lb-ft of torque. This specimen is equipped with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and the Sport Chrono Package Plus, ensuring optimized throttle mapping and dynamic engine mounts. The chassis utilizes Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) with a 10mm lower ride height, providing exceptional lateral stability and turn-in precision. Mechanically flawless, the car shows zero signs of bore scoring, and a recent DME report confirms a clean history with no overrevs beyond Zone 1. The exterior retains its original factory depth across all panels, while the cabin maintains its showroom-fresh matte finish on all switchgear and bolsters. This is a collector-grade example with a fully documented service trajectory.",
